title: Rubber Ducks In The Sun
content: The ducks were very happy to be in the sun. Off in the distance some clouds were forming.

title: Rubber Ducks In The Rain
content: The rain came and swept away the rubber ducks with little resistance, as they are inanimate objects.

title: Rubber Ducks In A Cave
content: The ducks took refuge in a cave because in this story they're sentient.

title: Choo Choo Train
content: Once upon a time, in a train yard there was a train that could run all day.

title: Train Tracks
content: Trains are cliche, how about we talk about the history of train tracks?
